title: [Dragonspine and Vultite]
description: Dragonspine Avenue ends here, and the canyon walls close in to the east and to the south.  A smaller street heads west, and several of those travelling it have the look of sailors.  A rough path wends its way east, sloping upward toward the canyon wall.
